      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant restoration or could serve as a donor for parts. The exterior shows extensive rust, paint peeling, and several body dents, while the interior has heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a cracked dashboard. Mechanically, the car is currently non-running and will need a complete overhaul of the engine and braking system. This is a project car for someone with the time and resources to bring it back to life.",
