    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in an uncompromising state, manifesting a showroom-equivalent aesthetic that satisfies the most rigorous standards of the discerning collector. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a history of climate-controlled storage and fastidious maintenance. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the conventional pre-owned market, offering an experience indistinguishable from its original delivery.",
